snippet.textDisplay: I honestly believe that this will be the biggest comeback ever! Black Swan was the first indication of this being an entirely new era in all of their career. EGO made me ecstatic and had me appreciating Hobi so much and looking at this tracklist makes me smile so much! BTS is being recognized all over the world, asked to be on numerous talk shows, and is collaborating with so many new and existing artists. All that we, as ARMY can do is give them all the love and support we can muster together. I won't lie this will be a bittersweet comeback due to Jin's enlistment soon, but in the words of Mr. Rogers, "Anything Manageable is Mentionable". Love and care for people in the world 💜
